metadata.name: Twin & Victor Wedding
metadata.description:
To commemorate the union and bond of Twin and Victor as they wedded on January 14th 2023 in an idyllic afternoon.

Twin and Victor celebrated the union of their hearts and lives in a beautiful wedding ceremony. Surrounded by their loved ones, the couple exchanged vows amidst a backdrop of beauty, pledging their love and devotion to each other for all eternity. As they shared their first dance as newlyweds, the joy and love that radiated from Victor and Twin was palpable, a testament to the deep bond they share.

It was a truly magical and unforgettable moment, one that will be forever etched in the hearts of all who were fortunate enough to witness it. May their union last forever just like this blockchain record.
